the unofficial launch of the holiday shopping

34:29.301 --> 34:34.506 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
season, special correspondent Mike Cerre reports
on a growing effort to expand the scope of

34:34.606 --> 34:40.745 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
seasonal giving to include charitable causes,
with a focus on one company turning bombs

34:40.845 --> 34:42.614 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
into bracelets.

34:42.714 --> 34:50.455 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
MIKE CERRE: Looking to escape the holiday
shopping madness, to give something more unique

34:50.555 --> 34:53.124 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
and meaningful this year?

34:53.224 --> 34:59.130 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
This coming Giving Tuesday, you can buy a
goat online through CARE USA to help an African

34:59.230 --> 35:05.904 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
family in need, or, closer to home, perhaps
some school supplies for your neighborhood

35:06.004 --> 35:10.208 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
school through DonorsChoose.com.

35:10.308 --> 35:14.980 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
For something a little more exotic, how about
jewelry handmade in Laos out of unexploded

35:15.080 --> 35:18.683 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
bombs to help the Mines Advisory Group clear
UXOs?

35:18.783 --> 35:20.919 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
HENRY TIMMS, Founder, Giving Tuesday: We know
about Black Friday.

35:21.019 --> 35:21.920 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
We know about Cyber Monday.

35:22.020 --> 35:23.755 align:left position:87.5%,start line:93.33% size:12.5%
We know they help stimulate our economy.

35:23.855 --> 35:25.290 align:left position:75%,start line:93.33% size:25%
But it felt like there was a missing gap.

35:25.390 --> 35:28.293 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
It felt like there was a moment to talk about
philanthropy and giving.

35:28.393 --> 35:30.061 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAN: For the arts.

35:30.161 --> 35:33.164 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
MIKE CERRE: It's called the giving season
for a reason.

35:33.264 --> 35:38.470 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
December is typically the most important month
for nonprofits all over the country.

35:38.570 --> 35:43.675 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Henry Timms started this online philanthropy
event four years ago out of New York's 92nd

35:43.775 --> 35:45.710 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Street Y.

35:45.810 --> 35:49.848 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
