countries.

35:49.948 --> 35:58.490 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Last year, over 700,000 holiday shoppers pledged
more than $110 million to their favorite charities,

35:58.590 --> 36:00.358 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
big and small.

36:00.458 --> 36:03.561 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
HENRY TIMMS: One of the things we have always
seen -- and we see it more now with social

36:03.661 --> 36:06.464 align:left position:75%,start line:93.33% size:25%
